{"tid":945364,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有另一半既，好心就唔好上交友apps啦","createTime":"2018-12-17T23:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T12:03:28.000Z","uid":162223,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf41f7a30e115dd73c242ec1a775c4810a4dbeaf","tid":945364,"uid":162223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:07:07.000Z","msg":"由於生活圈子太細，根本冇咩機會識到異性<br />\n交友apps其實真係一個好途徑去識可發展既異性<br />\n有時match到啲好岩傾，覺得可以發展落去既異性啦，點知原來係有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母果下真係好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢點解仲要玩交友apps啦，佢話想揾人傾下計，而且男朋友都知佢上，只要大家都相信對方就ok，雙方都要有自己既社交圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗有自己社交圈子唔會係叫你上交友apps識多啲仔，同其他男仔傾計下化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲對話仲要好曖味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為自己有機會岀pool既時候，對方已經有男朋友，仲話只係揾人吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多人上得交友apps既都岀pool，你估真係只想識朋友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持另一半上交友apps既小心帽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直程瞞住男/女朋友玩既就食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457ef9c077469802fee1ee3df77bfc0b165c421d","tid":945364,"uid":195364,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:20:53.000Z","msg":"你咪又係見人靚先add人add著個姣婆啫，用得交友app就一早問定人有冇男朋友啦"},{"pid":"889e761111b7ec41d66ee15a3263832a3682b080","tid":945364,"uid":3501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:34:46.000Z","msg":"下次問清楚啦<br />\n雖然我都唔知有男女朋友仲玩交友apps係咩心態<br />\n扮明係食仔食女用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.